<A>__{kate's mum continues to spy. pov: the neighbour bends down out of sight. on rising again, he sees maggie at the window and waves. maggie flinches, before dropping the curtain.}
<L>__{interior pub dusk}
<A>__{kate comes through the door. oonagh sits on her own at a booth. kate joins her.}
<C>__{kate}
<D>__{sorry i'm late.}
<C>__{oonagh}
<D>__{don't tell me...}
